{"tid":2102274,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"彭博：中國開始對國民全球徵稅","createTime":"2020-07-10T10:51:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-12T14:00:04.000Z","uid":53062,"like":99,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":51,"replies":[{"pid":"4e6a438b41d9c79a790af0b804feaafe178ec529","tid":2102274,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T10:51:26.000Z","msg":"學美國全球徵稅，又回血<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nChina Starts Taxing Its Citizens for Global Income<br />\n<br />\nChina has started tracking down some of its citizens living abroad to collect taxes, surprising expatriates who never had to pay levies back home on overseas income, according to people familiar with the matter.<br />\n<br />\nState-owned enterprises operating in Hong Kong, which has one of the lowest tax rates in the world, told mainland Chinese expats recently to declare their 2019 income so they can pay taxes at home, according to the people, who asked not be named because they aren&rsquo;t authorized to speak publicly on the matter. Chinese SOEs are also informing employees working in other places such as Singapore, two of the people said.<br />\n<br />\n.......<br />\n<br />\nIt&rsquo;s not just paychecks. The rules also subject income from dividends and property sales to taxation back home, said Jia Zeliang, chief executive officer at wealth-planning adviser Ishtar Consulting Inc. That&rsquo;s likely to force many companies to shoulder much of the extra tax burden or risk an exodus of Chinese expats, Jia said.<br />\n<br />\n.......<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n&mdash; With assistance by Shirley Zhao, Jun Luo, Jinshan Hong, Lulu Yilun Chen, and Kiuyan Wong<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2020-07-10/china-starts-taxing-its-citizens-global-income-for-first-time\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2020-07-10%2Fchina-starts-taxing-its-citizens-global-income-for-first-time&d=Wd2ZpPw6abVmqVF%2BhWwummipy2YcCk4ac690EPkq9Sw%3D&h=0e39c1e5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2020-07-10/china-starts-taxing-its-citizens-global-income-for-first-time</a>"},{"pid":"b93f461e70af83a93edbaa5aeaee3cf5cd29ada5","tid":2102274,"uid":262674,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T10:58:53.000Z","msg":"收割 <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/q5TRYnj.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fq5TRYnj.gif&h=de7e77ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n韮菜 <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RCU9K2y.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRCU9K2y.gif&h=d83301f8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2be6416bb215a4ea7d644304c11243a459eab260","tid":2102274,"uid":359022,"like":71,"dislike":0,"score":71,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T11:00:01.000Z","msg":"不論在哪裡 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你的護照 會帶你的錢回國<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"701e97b1d23a4e3d71ef4574d4943013f062210d","tid":2102274,"uid":125310,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T13:18:49.000Z","msg":"bloomberg<br />\n人民幣成為世界避險資產 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2020-07-09/yuan-morphs-into-global-risk-bellwether-as-china-leads-recovery\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2020-07-09%2Fyuan-morphs-into-global-risk-bellwether-as-china-leads-recovery&d=Wd2ZpPw6abVmqVF%2BhWwummipy2YcCk4ac690EPkq9Sw%3D